1.0.name: wordpress/gmaptip
1.0.description: gMapTip is a Google Maps Plug-in. With gMapTip you can easily add Tooltips to your post to let everyone know where he/she can find shops, restaurants, etz. in his/her environment or just show everyone where something in this world is located. For more information visit: http://www.gnomx.at/gmaptip
